title.narrative: More women are economically empowered, have access to decent work and safe migration, and are able to advance their role in development, peace- and resilience building

description.narrative: The outcome will focus on increasing women’s livelihood security, access to decent work and safe migration. The work under this outcome will: (a) establish partnerships with private sector, women’s cooperatives/business leaders and government institutions on gender-responsive financial inclusion, improved market access, decent work and new sources of income for women; (b) enable key stakeholders to implement evidence-based policies and essential services to end violence against women migrant workers and promote safety and empowerment.
